    Title: Tejo-bindu Upanishad
    Locus: I 23
Tags:
  - Discernment-Truth=The Void=Solitude
  - Discernment-Truth=Reality=The Motionless Mover
  - Discernment-Truth=The Eye Of Eternity-Supreme Center=The Eye of the Heart
---
That place which is everywhere at all times present (being the basis of all
that evolves) and in which, in the beginning, at the end or in the middle,
there is no living creature, that place (which is their own Self, the yogis)
call ‘Solitude’.
